Sept 8 (Reuters) - The following financial services industry appointments were announced on Monday. To inform us of other job changes, email moves@thomsonreuters.com.

SBERBANK CIB The corporate and investment banking business of Russia's Sberbank <SBER.MM> said it appointed Sergey Smirnov head of government and municipal project and programmes division in its client management department. [ID:nL3N0R92KS]  SCHRODERS PLC <SDR.L> The asset manager said it appointed Matt Hudson to manage its UK Opportunities fund. [ID:nL3N0R92I9]  TOWERS WATSON & CO <TW.N>  The provider of human resources and risk and financial management services, appointed Luba Nikulina global head of manager research. [ID:nL3N0R925X]  TMF GROUP